            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Domino nostro clemen<lb break="no" n="2"/>tissimo principi <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Iulio</del> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">Crispo nobilissimo ac <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></del><lb break="no" n="4"/><del rend="erasure">tissimo Caesari</del> <lb n="5"/>Iulius Aurelianus <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Camp</abbr><ex>aniae</ex></expan> devotus numini maiestati<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="7"/>eius
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Z. 3-5: AE 1969/70, Guadagno: Fl(avio) Iulio [Constanti nobi]lissimo ac [aman]tissimo (bzw. [amant]issimo) [omnium] Caesari. Die Statuenbasis ist Crispus und nicht Constans gewidmet.</p>
            </div>
